  <div class="rounded-xl border border-teal-200 bg-teal-50 p-4 mb-8">
    <p class="text-sm font-bold text-teal-900 mb-1">15% Evaluation Profit Bonus</p>
    <p class="text-sm text-teal-800">
      A <strong>15% bonus</strong> of your combined Phase 1 and Phase 2 profits is added to the starting balance of your Funded Star Account once you reach 10% growth. This rewards strong evaluation performance with additional funded capital.
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- ─── Inactivity Rule ─────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <div class="rounded-xl border border-amber-200 bg-amber-50 p-4 mb-8">
    <p class="text-sm font-bold text-amber-900 mb-1">Inactivity Rule</p>
    <p class="text-sm text-amber-800">
      Accounts are deactivated after <strong>30 calendar days</strong> of inactivity. To reset the inactivity timer, a trade must stay open for at least <strong>1 minute (60 seconds)</strong>.
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- ─── Paid Add-Ons ───────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Paid Add-Ons</h3>
  <p class="mb-4">
    If you want to customise your funded account, BrightFunded offers one of the best selections of paid addons available. You can modify your profit payouts, evaluation process, and fees:
  </p>

  <div class="overflow-x-auto rounded-xl border border-slate-200 mb-8">
    <table class="w-full text-sm whitespace-nowrap">
      <thead class="bg-slate-50 text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wide">
