    For crypto, Bitcoin spreads start as low as <strong>$0.1</strong> and average about <strong>$1</strong>, which is far better than the $5 to $10 crypto spreads you'll find at other firms. Other popular digital assets like Ethereum also come in tight, and indices and commodities follow suit, with pricing aggregated from sources like S&P, Nasdaq, ICE, and FTSE to mirror real time market conditions.
  </p>

  <!-- Spreads overview -->
  <div class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-4 gap-2 mb-8">
